---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Refer Jeremy | Scripture Alive Ministry"
  description="Refer Jeremy Kluth to others to help him bless and equip more people to memorize Scripture."
  ogImage="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/vxczpihg/production/77e01b90ecf67d8a98bd7b81065106b062648bf3-354x177.webp"
>

  <main class="w-full">

    <section class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 md:py-16">

      <div class="text-center mb-6">
        <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary">
          Scripture Alive Referral Form
        </h1>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          When you give us information about a church or group, we will reach out and connect with them by phone and email. We'll tell them all about <strong>Jeremy Kluth</strong> and invite them to our next public performance so they can see what we do for themselves. Please know that by referring an organization, there is no obligation on their part, we will simply introduce our ministry to them.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-10">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <img
            src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/vxczpihg/production/77e01b90ecf67d8a98bd7b81065106b062648bf3-354x177.webp"
            alt="Scripture Performances"
            loading="lazy"
            class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center bg-black/30">
            <span class="text-white font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-lg italic">Scripture Performances</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <img
            src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/vxczpihg/production/adab64545b5f89913fecdfea364d41c884f063cc-354x177.webp"
            alt="Scripture Memory Workshops"
            loading="lazy"
            class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center bg-black/30">
            <span class="text-white font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-lg italic">Scripture Memory Workshops</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <img
            src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/vxczpihg/production/8e31433446554b2eb54ea4a475dec26aa0af6dcd-354x177.webp"
            alt="Guest Preaching"
            loading="lazy"
            class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center bg-black/30">
            <span class="text-white font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-lg italic">Guest Preaching</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="w-full rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-blue-200" style="box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
        <iframe
          src="https://mail.spiritmediaone.com/widget/form/FAIca66I1ZhNOtTZxCPq"
          class="w-full border-0"
          style="height:2583px"
          id="inline-FAIca66I1ZhNOtTZxCPq"
          data-layout="{'id':'INLINE'}"
          data-trigger-type="alwaysShow"
          data-trigger-value=""
          data-activation-type="alwaysActivated"
          data-activation-value=""
          data-deactivation-type="neverDeactivate"
          data-deactivation-value=""
          data-form-name="Scripture Alive Referral Form"
          data-height="2583"
          data-layout-iframe-id="inline-FAIca66I1ZhNOtTZxCPq"
          data-form-id="FAIca66I1ZhNOtTZxCPq"
          title="Scripture Alive Referral Form"
        ></iframe>
      </div>

    </section>

  </main>

</Layout>